p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Retrieve objects of a specific type
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
Retrieve objects of a specific data type. The resulting `Query` object can be further refined using filters, sorts and by following relations.

A query must then be *executed* or *observed* to actually return results.
The data type of the objects to be queried
A query object that can be further refined, executed, or observed
Add the instances to the result. (automatically added if there is no other data type to the query, for example added by a "Query Follow Relation" brick)
